HEADWORD: Spathic
<hw>Spath"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>spathique</ets>, fr. F. & G. <ets>spath</ets> spar.]</ety>
<def>Like spar; foliated or lamellar; spathose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

